data.description: Don't let this home pass you by. The home has had to total remodel, the exterior features new vinyl siding, new architectural shingled roof, new sidewalk w/ concrete steps. When you enter the home new Luxury wide Plank Flooring throughout the entire home all new lighting features. The kitchen has new cabinets & kitchen island new granite countertops with black stainless-steel appliances and recessed lighting. There are 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The primary bedroom has its own private bathroom. There is a pull-down stairway with a floored attic and shed located in the backyard for extra storage. Call today for a private showing.
